rtists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格（Liam Gallager）</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-hints-that-his-new-album-is-done-3499289">向一位歌迷暗示他的下一张个人专辑已经完成</a>。</p><p>这位创作歌手的最新录音室唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/liam-gallagher-cmon-you-know-3231721">《C&#39;mon You Know》</a>于 2022 年发行。</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔</a>最近透露，他已经与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camelphat">CamelPhat</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-has-recorded-a-secret-dance-track-3500259">录制了一首秘密舞曲</a>，但尚未完成。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/coronavirus">新冠疫情</a>封锁期间，诺埃尔罕见地与其他几位艺术家合作创作新音乐<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-and-dizzee-rascal-have-worked-on-a-new-track-together-2775386">，包括与迪兹·拉斯卡尔 (Dizzee Rascal)</a>和伊梅尔达·梅 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/imelda-may-just-one-kiss-video-noel-gallagher-ronnie-wood-2866793">Imelda May)</a>合作。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-oasis-new-music-video-for-acquiesce-3502388">查看 Oasis 的新音乐视频“Acquiesce”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
